: "portfolio.testimonial", "pk": 3, "fields": {"client_name": "Courage Banda", "client_role": "Forex Sheriff", "content": "From concept to final cut, the process was smooth and well-organized. We’ll definitely work together again.", "client_image": "testimonials/meet-696077_640.jpg", "created_at": "2025-12-27T16:58:26.005Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.blogpost", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "Behind the Scenes of a Successful Production", "slug": "behind-the-scenes-of-a-successful-production", "content": "When audiences watch a polished video or film, they often see only the final result. What they don’t see is the planning, coordination, and creative problem-solving that happens behind the scenes.\r\n\r\nA successful production begins long before the camera starts rolling. Pre-production involves concept development, scripting, storyboarding, location scouting, and assembling the right team. This phase sets the foundation for everything that follows.\r\n\r\nDuring production, every detail matters—from lighting and sound to camera movement and performance direction. Clear communication between the director, crew, and talent ensures that the vision remains consistent throughout the shoot.\r\n\r\nFinally, post-production brings the project to life. Editing, color grading, sound design, and visual effects refine the raw footage into a compelling final product. This stage is where storytelling truly shines.\r\n\r\nAt our production company, we believe great content is built through preparation, creativity, and collaboration. Every project we deliver reflects our commitment to quality and storytelling.", "featured_image": "blog/gimbal-7447264.jpg", "author_name": "XMP Team", "is_published": true, "created_at": "2025-12-27T16:24:20.041Z", "updated_at": "2025-12-27T16:24:20.041Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.blogpost", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Why Professional Video Content Matters for Your Brand", "slug": "why-professional-video-content-matters-for-your-brand", "content": "In today’s digital world, video content is one of the most powerful tools a brand can use to connect with its audience. From social media to corporate websites, video captures attention faster and communicates messages more effectively than text alone.\r\n\r\nProfessional video production helps establish credibility. High-quality visuals, clear audio, and strong storytelling show your audience that your brand takes itself seriously. It builds trust and leaves a lasting impression.\r\n\r\nVideo also increases engagement. Whether it’s a promotional video, product showcase, or brand story, professionally produced content encourages viewers to watch longer, share more, and take action.\r\n\r\nInvesting in professional video isn’t just about looking good—it’s about communicating your message clearly, creatively, and consistently. When done right, video becomes a powerful asset for long-term brand growth.", "featured_image": "blog/video-editing-6834406.jpg", "author_name": "XMP Team", "is_published": true, "created_at": "2025-12-27T16:29:06.101Z", "updated_at": "2025-12-27T16:29:06.101Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.blogpost", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "The Importance of Pre-Production Planning", "slug": "the-importance-of-pre-production-planning", "content": "Many people assume production starts when the cameras roll, but the real work begins much earlier. Pre-production is where ideas are refined and potential challenges are solved before they become costly problems.\r\n\r\nThis stage includes defining objectives, writing scripts, creating shot lists, scheduling, and budgeting. Proper planning ensures that everyone involved understands their role and the overall vision of the project.\r\n\r\nStrong pre-production saves time, reduces stress on set, and results in better creative outcomes. It allows the production team to focus on storytelling rather than troubleshooting.\r\n\r\nSimply put, the better the preparation, the smoother the production.", "featured_image": "blog/people-2577669.jpg", "author_name": "XMP Team", "is_published": true, "created_at": "2025-12-27T16:35:09.462Z", "updated_at": "2025-12-27T16:35:09.462Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.livestream", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "XMP", "description": "Testing the Feature", "stream_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/4nrelQSnDHc?si=Jm_J6yv1M-nCBi80", "is_live": false, "scheduled_at": null, "created_at": "2025-12-28T11:41:51.973Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.livestream", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "XMP Soccer", "description": "Live Match Broadcast", "stream_url": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/U5X258iDI0s?si=epsuUUKGiHPv024K", "is_live": false, "scheduled_at": null, "created_at": "2025-12-28T11:56:29.253Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.teammember", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Max Zvikomborero", "role": "Director of Photography", "image": "team/Max-Zvikomborero.jpg", "created_at": "2025-12-28T10:00:56.531Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.teammember", "pk": 2, "fields": {"name": "Everton Musekiwa", "role": "Video Editor & Colorist", "image": "team/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-03_at_5.31.08_PM.jpeg", "created_at": "2025-12-28T10:07:31.440Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.teammember", "pk": 3, "fields": {"name": "Tafadzwa Njagu", "role": "Web Systems developer", "image": "team/tnjagu.jpeg", "created_at": "2025-12-28T10:24:14.935Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.teammember", "pk": 4, "fields": {"name": "Shawn Mabamba", "role": "Director", "image": "team/Shaun.jpeg", "created_at": "2025-12-28T10:34:13.725Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.pricingplan", "pk": 1, "fields": {"service_type": "video", "plan_name": "Professional Video", "price": "600", "features": "Up to 5 hours of filming\nMulti-camera setup\nProfessional lighting & audio\n2–4 minute edited video\nMotion graphics & titles\nFull HD / 4K delivery\n2 revisions", "is_popular": true, "order": 2, "created_at": "2025-12-28T21:05:03.496Z"}}, {"model": "portfolio.pricingplan", "pk": 2, "fields": {"service_type": "video", "plan_name": "Basic Video", "price": "250", "features"